high_descs: Turn left and move to the counter with the toaster.
Open the upper right cabinet above the toaster and remove the black plate.
Turn to the right and head to the fridge.
Put the plate in the fridge next to the lettuce, close the door for a few seconds and then take the plate back out.
Turn around and walk across the room to the brown tiered shelving unit to your left in the corner.
Put the plate on the second shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled plate on the brown tiered shelving unit.

high_descs: Turn to your left and approach the counter in front of you
Open the cabinet above your head and take out the black plate
Turn to the right and walk towards the black fridge on the other side of the room
Open the fridge and place the plate next to the lettuce. Shut the door for a while before taking it back out and closing the fridge again.
Turn to your left away from the fridge and walk left past the white stove to the wooden shelf
Place the plate on the shelf in the middle
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled plate onto the wooden shelf in the kitchen

high_descs: Turn around and look up to the cabinets.
Open the right cabinet and take out a plate.
Turn right and head towards the fridge.
Place the plate next to the lettuce in the fridge for it to cool and then take it back out.
Turn around towards the stove, make a left towards the wooden shelves.
Place the plate on the second shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled plate on the wooden shelves.
